{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881080012,"sessionID":"ses_2853db339ffeQJuEq2GpPsIUmw","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac2cc9a001LzDxd07Rg4fuCk","messageID":"msg_d7ac2afe3001nUrW5arYysoNzZ","sessionID":"ses_2853db339ffeQJuEq2GpPsIUmw","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-b36409bf739e428daa9b6153e0bdd19f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"cat /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-030/* 2>/dev/null | head -100","description":"Read AR-030 change files"},"output":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-030\n- **Title**: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n- **Module**: manifests\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: L\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nCreate Helm chart templates and values files for deploying AgentCube components.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Delta Specification\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis delta specification provides comprehensive acceptance criteria for the Helm Chart templates and Values configuration for deploying the AgentCube platform components. It extends the base deployment specifications with detailed GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios for all chart operations, configuration options, and lifecycle management.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata validation\n\nThe system SHALL provide a valid Helm Chart.yaml with proper metadata and version information.\n\n#### Scenario: Chart.yaml contains required metadata fields\n- **GIVEN** a Helm chart directory structure exists\n- **WHEN** the Chart.yaml file is present\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain fields: apiVersion, name, description, type, version, appVersion\n- **AND** apiVersion SHALL be set to v2\n- **AND** type SHALL be set to application\n- **AND** version SHALL follow semantic versioning (e.g., 1.0.0)\n\n#### Scenario: Chart keywords and maintainers are present\n- **GIVEN** a valid Chart.yaml file\n- **WHEN** inspecting the chart metadata\n- **THEN** keywords SHALL include relevant terms: agentcube, ai, code-interpreter, agent-runtime\n- **AND** maintainers SHALL be defined with name and email fields\n\n### Requirement: Default values.yaml structure\n\nThe system SHALL provide a comprehensive default values.yaml with all configurable parameters.\n\n#### Scenario: Global configuration section exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the global configuration section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: imageRegistry, imagePullSecrets, namespace, labels\n- **AND** imageRegistry SHALL default to empty string (allow Docker Hub)\n- **AND** imagePullSecrets SHALL default to empty list\n- **AND** namespace SHALL default to agentcube\n\n#### Scenario: Controller Manager configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the controllerManager section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 2\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/controller-manager\n- **AND** image.pullPolicy SHALL default to IfNotPresent\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the workloadManager section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 2\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/workload-manager\n\n#### Scenario: Router configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the router section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 3\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/router\n\n#### Scenario: RBAC configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the rbac section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: create field\n- **AND** create SHALL default to true\n\n#### Scenario: Monitoring configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the monitoring section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled and serviceMonitor fields\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to false\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.enabled SHALL default to false\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.interval SHALL default to 30s\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.scrapeTimeout SHALL default to 10s\n\n#### Scenario: Security contexts are configured\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the security context sections\n- **THEN** podSecurityContext SHALL include: runAsNonRoot, runAsUser, fsGroup\n- **AND** runAsNonRoot SHALL default to true\n","metadata":{"output":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-030\n- **Title**: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n- **Module**: manifests\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: L\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nCreate Helm chart templates and values files for deploying AgentCube components.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Delta Specification\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis delta specification provides comprehensive acceptance criteria for the Helm Chart templates and Values configuration for deploying the AgentCube platform components. It extends the base deployment specifications with detailed GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios for all chart operations, configuration options, and lifecycle management.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata validation\n\nThe system SHALL provide a valid Helm Chart.yaml with proper metadata and version information.\n\n#### Scenario: Chart.yaml contains required metadata fields\n- **GIVEN** a Helm chart directory structure exists\n- **WHEN** the Chart.yaml file is present\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain fields: apiVersion, name, description, type, version, appVersion\n- **AND** apiVersion SHALL be set to v2\n- **AND** type SHALL be set to application\n- **AND** version SHALL follow semantic versioning (e.g., 1.0.0)\n\n#### Scenario: Chart keywords and maintainers are present\n- **GIVEN** a valid Chart.yaml file\n- **WHEN** inspecting the chart metadata\n- **THEN** keywords SHALL include relevant terms: agentcube, ai, code-interpreter, agent-runtime\n- **AND** maintainers SHALL be defined with name and email fields\n\n### Requirement: Default values.yaml structure\n\nThe system SHALL provide a comprehensive default values.yaml with all configurable parameters.\n\n#### Scenario: Global configuration section exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the global configuration section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: imageRegistry, imagePullSecrets, namespace, labels\n- **AND** imageRegistry SHALL default to empty string (allow Docker Hub)\n- **AND** imagePullSecrets SHALL default to empty list\n- **AND** namespace SHALL default to agentcube\n\n#### Scenario: Controller Manager configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the controllerManager section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 2\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/controller-manager\n- **AND** image.pullPolicy SHALL default to IfNotPresent\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the workloadManager section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 2\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/workload-manager\n\n#### Scenario: Router configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the router section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled, replicaCount, image, service, resources, nodeSelector, tolerations, affinity\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to true\n- **AND** replicaCount SHALL default to 3\n- **AND** image.repository SHALL default to agentcube/router\n\n#### Scenario: RBAC configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the rbac section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: create field\n- **AND** create SHALL default to true\n\n#### Scenario: Monitoring configuration exists\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the monitoring section\n- **THEN** it SHALL include: enabled and serviceMonitor fields\n- **AND** enabled SHALL default to false\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.enabled SHALL default to false\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.interval SHALL default to 30s\n- **AND** serviceMonitor.scrapeTimeout SHALL default to 10s\n\n#### Scenario: Security contexts are configured\n- **GIVEN** the default values.yaml file\n- **WHEN** reading the security context sections\n- **THEN** podSecurityContext SHALL include: runAsNonRoot, runAsUser, fsGroup\n- **AND** runAsNonRoot SHALL default to true\n","exit":0,"description":"Read AR-030 change files","truncated":false},"title":"Read AR-030 change files","time":{"start":1775881079995,"end":1775881080011}}}}
