{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881083381,"sessionID":"ses_2853db339ffeQJuEq2GpPsIUmw","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac2d9d0001XZTucDcoeW0V0g","messageID":"msg_d7ac2cd060016Nv9yvgMdhJRT0","sessionID":"ses_2853db339ffeQJuEq2GpPsIUmw","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4149167e76c74d8689f794979405b9c5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-030/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-030/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: Helm Chart for AgentCube platform provides a standardized, configurable, and reusable Kubernetes deployment solution. The chart encapsulates all necessary Kubernetes resources (CRDs, Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, RBAC) and enables flexible configuration through Values files, simplifying deployment across multiple environments.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `manifests`  \n8: **Language:** YAML + Go Templates  \n9: **Source Root:** `manifests/charts/agentcube/`  \n10: **Size:** L\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Chart Structure\n15: \n16: ```\n17: agentcube/\n18: ├── Chart.yaml                          # Chart metadata\n19: ├── values.yaml                         # Default configuration\n20: ├── values-dev.yaml                     # Development environment overrides\n21: ├── values-prod.yaml                    # Production environment overrides\n22: ├── values-test.yaml                    # Test environment overrides\n23: ├── templates/\n24: │   ├── crds/\n25: │   │   ├── agentruntime.yaml           # AgentRuntime CRD\n26: │   │   └── codeinterpreter.yaml        # CodeInterpreter CRD\n27: │   ├── controller-manager/\n28: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Controller Manager deployment\n29: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Controller Manager service\n30: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Controller Manager service account\n31: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Controller Manager RBAC rules\n32: │   ├── workload-manager/\n33: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Workload Manager deployment\n34: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Workload Manager service\n35: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Workload Manager service account\n36: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Workload Manager RBAC rules\n37: │   ├── router/\n38: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Router deployment\n39: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Router service\n40: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Router service account\n41: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Router RBAC rules\n42: │   ├── rbac/\n43: │   │   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # Cluster-wide role\n44: │   │   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # Cluster-wide role binding\n45: │   ├── monitoring/\n46: │   │   └── servicemonitor.yaml         # Prometheus ServiceMonitor\n47: │   ├── configmaps/\n48: │   │   └── config.yaml                 # Application configuration\n49: │   ├── secrets/\n50: │   │   └── secret.yaml                 # Sensitive configuration\n51: │   ├── networkpolicies/\n52: │   │   └── networkpolicy.yaml          # Network access control\n53: │   ├── poddisruptionbudgets/\n54: │   │   ├── controller-manager.yaml\n55: │   │   ├── workload-manager.yaml\n56: │   │   └── router.yaml\n57: │   ├── NOTES.txt                       # Installation notes\n58: │   ├── _helpers.tpl                    # Template helpers\n59: │   └── ingress.yaml                    # Ingress configuration\n60: ├── tests/\n61: │   ├── controller-manager_test.yaml\n62: │   ├── workload-manager_test.yaml\n63: │   └── router_test.yaml\n64: └── README.md                           # Chart documentation\n65: ```\n66: \n67: ### Component Interactions\n68: \n69: ```\n70: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n71: │                      Helm Chart                             │\n72: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n73: │  │   CRDs       │  │  Controller  │  │   Workload   │     │\n74: │  │              │  │   Manager    │  │   Manager    │     │\n75: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n76: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n77: │  │    Router    │  │    RBAC      │  │  Monitoring  │     │\n78: │  │              │  │              │  │              │     │\n79: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n80: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n81:                               │\n82:                               │ helm install/upgrade\n83:                               ▼\n84: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n85: │                   Kubernetes Cluster                        │\n86: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n87: │  │              API Server + etcd                       │  │\n88: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n89: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n90: │  │  Controller  │  │   Workload   │  │    Router    │     │\n91: │  │   Manager    │  │   Manager    │  │              │     │\n92: │  │   (Pods)     │  │   (Pods)     │  │   (Pods)     │     │\n93: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n94: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n95: │  │   Services   │  │     CRDs     │  │   Secrets/   │     │\n96: │  │              │  │              │  │  ConfigMaps  │     │\n97: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n98: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n99: ```\n100: \n101: ## Data Structures\n102: \n103: ### Chart.yaml\n104: \n105: ```yaml\n106: apiVersion: v2\n107: name: agentcube\n108: description: Helm chart for AgentCube platform - Kubernetes-native AI agent runtime and code interpreter\n109: type: application\n110: version: 1.0.0\n111: appVersion: \"1.0.0\"\n112: keywords:\n113:   - agentcube\n114:   - ai\n115:   - code-interpreter\n116:   - agent-runtime\n117:   - kubernetes\n118: maintainers:\n119:   - name: AgentCube Team\n120:     email: team@agentcube.io\n121: home: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n122: sources:\n123:   - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n124: icon: https://agentcube.io/logo.svg\n125: annotations:\n126:   artifacthub.io/category: ai-machine-learning\n127:   artifacthub.io/license: Apache-2.0\n128:   artifacthub.io/operator: \"false\"\n129: ```\n130: \n131: ### Values.yaml Hierarchy\n132: \n133: ```yaml\n134: # Global configuration applied to all components\n135: global:\n136:   imageRegistry: docker.io\n137:   imagePullSecrets: []\n138:   namespaceOverride: agentcube\n139:   labels: {}\n140:   annotations: {}\n141: \n142: # Image pull policy for all components\n143: imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n144: \n145: # Controller Manager configuration\n146: controllerManager:\n147:   enabled: true\n148:   replicaCount: 2\n149:   image:\n150:     repository: agentcube/controller-manager\n151:     tag: v1.0.0\n152:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n153:   service:\n154:     type: ClusterIP\n155:     port: 8080\n156:     targetPort: 8080\n157:     annotations: {}\n158:   resources:\n159:     requests:\n160:       cpu: 100m\n161:       memory: 128Mi\n162:     limits:\n163:       cpu: 500m\n164:       memory: 512Mi\n165:   nodeSelector: {}\n166:   tolerations: []\n167:   affinity: {}\n168:   podAnnotations: {}\n169:   podLabels: {}\n170:   securityContext:\n171:     runAsNonRoot: true\n172:     runAsUser: 1000\n173:     fsGroup: 1000\n174:   containerSecurityContext:\n175:     allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\n176:     capabilities:\n177:       drop:\n178:         - ALL\n179:     readOnlyRootFilesystem: true\n180:   livenessProbe:\n181:     httpGet:\n182:       path: /healthz\n183:       port: 8080\n184:     initialDelaySeconds: 30\n185:     periodSeconds: 10\n186:     timeoutSeconds: 5\n187:     failureThreshold: 3\n188:     successThreshold: 1\n189:   readinessProbe:\n190:     httpGet:\n191:       path: /readyz\n192:       port: 8080\n193:     initialDelaySeconds: 10\n194:     periodSeconds: 5\n195:     timeoutSeconds: 3\n196:     failureThreshold: 3\n197:     successThreshold: 1\n198:   autoscaling:\n199:     enabled: false\n200:     minReplicas: 2\n201:     maxReplicas: 5\n202:     targetCPUUtilizationPercentage: 80\n203:     targetMemoryUtilizationPercentage: 80\n204:   podDisruptionBudget:\n205:     enabled: true\n206:     minAvailable: 1\n207:   env: []\n208:   envFrom: []\n209:   extraVolumeMounts: []\n210:   extraVolumes: []\n211:   serviceAccount:\n212:     create: true\n213:     name: \"\"\n214:     annotations: {}\n215:   rbac:\n216:     create: true\n217:     rules: []\n218: \n219: # Workload Manager configuration\n220: workloadManager:\n221:   enabled: true\n222:   replicaCount: 2\n223:   image:\n224:     repository: agentcube/workload-manager\n225:     tag: v1.0.0\n226:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n227:   service:\n228:     type: ClusterIP\n229:     port: 8080\n230:     targetPort: 8080\n231:     annotations: {}\n232:   resources:\n233:     requests:\n234:       cpu: 200m\n235:       memory: 256Mi\n236:     limits:\n237:       cpu: 1000m\n238:       memory: 1Gi\n239:   nodeSelector: {}\n240:   tolerations: []\n241:   affinity: {}\n242:   podAnnotations: {}\n243:   podLabels: {}\n244:   securityContext:\n245:     runAsNonRoot: true\n246:     runAsUser: 1000\n247:     fsGroup: 1000\n248:   containerSecurityContext:\n249:     allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\n250:     capabilities:\n251:       drop:\n252:         - ALL\n253:     readOnlyRootFilesystem: true\n254:   livenessProbe:\n255:     httpGet:\n256:       path: /healthz\n257:       port: 8080\n258:     initialDelaySeconds: 30\n259:     periodSeconds: 10\n260:     timeoutSeconds: 5\n261:     failureThreshold: 3\n262:   readinessProbe:\n263:     httpGet:\n264:       path: /readyz\n265:       port: 8080\n266:     initialDelaySeconds: 10\n267:     periodSeconds: 5\n268:     timeoutSeconds: 3\n269:     failureThreshold: 3\n270:   autoscaling:\n271:     enabled: false\n272:     minReplicas: 2\n273:     maxReplicas: 10\n274:     targetCPUUtilizationPercentage: 75\n275:     targetMemoryUtilizationPercentage: 80\n276:   podDisruptionBudget:\n277:     enabled: true\n278:     minAvailable: 1\n279:   env: []\n280:   envFrom: []\n281:   extraVolumeMounts: []\n282:   extraVolumes: []\n283:   serviceAccount:\n284:     create: true\n285:     name: \"\"\n286:     annotations: {}\n287:   rbac:\n288:     create: true\n289:     rules: []\n290: \n291: # Router configuration\n292: router:\n293:   enabled: true\n294:   replicaCount: 3\n295:   image:\n296:     repository: agentcube/router\n297:     tag: v1.0.0\n298:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n299:   service:\n300:     type: ClusterIP\n301:     port: 8080\n302:     targetPort: 8080\n303:     annotations: {}\n304:     loadBalancerSourceRanges: []\n305:   ingress:\n306:     enabled: false\n307:     className: nginx\n308:     annotations: {}\n309:     hosts:\n310:       - host: agentcube.example.com\n311:         paths:\n312:           - path: /\n313:             pathType: Prefix\n314:     tls:\n315:       - secretName: agentcube-tls\n316:         hosts:\n317:           - agentcube.example.com\n318:   resources:\n319:     requests:\n320:       cpu: 150m\n321:       memory: 192Mi\n322:     limits:\n323:       cpu: 750m\n324:       memory: 768Mi\n325:   nodeSelector: {}\n326:   tolerations: []\n327:   affinity:\n328:     podAntiAffinity:\n329:       requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:\n330:       - labelSelector:\n331:           matchLabels:\n332:             app.kubernetes.io/component: router\n333:         topologyKey: kubernetes.io/hostname\n334:   podAnnotations: {}\n335:   podLabels: {}\n336:   securityContext:\n337:     runAsNonRoot: true\n338:     runAsUser: 1000\n339:     fsGroup: 1000\n340:   containerSecurityContext:\n341:     allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\n342:     capabilities:\n343:       drop:\n344:         - ALL\n345:     readOnlyRootFilesystem: true\n346:   livenessProbe:\n347:     httpGet:\n348:       path: /healthz\n349:       port: 8080\n350:     initialDelaySeconds: 30\n351:     periodSeconds: 10\n352:     timeoutSeconds: 5\n353:     failureThreshold: 3\n354:   readinessProbe:\n355:     httpGet:\n356:       path: /readyz\n357:       port: 8080\n358:     initialDelaySeconds: 10\n359:     periodSeconds: 5\n360:     timeoutSeconds: 3\n361:     failureThreshold: 3\n362:   autoscaling:\n363:     enabled: false\n364:     minReplicas: 3\n365:     maxReplicas: 10\n366:     targetCPUUtilizationPercentage: 70\n367:     targetMemoryUtilizationPercentage: 75\n368:   podDisruptionBudget:\n369:     enabled: true\n370:     minAvailable: 2\n371:   env: []\n372:   envFrom: []\n373:   extraVolumeMounts: []\n374:   extraVolumes: []\n375:   serviceAccount:\n376:     create: true\n377:     name: \"\"\n378:     annotations: {}\n379:   rbac:\n380:     create: true\n381:     rules: []\n382: \n383: # Global RBAC configuration\n384: rbac:\n385:   create: true\n386:   clusterRole:\n387:     create: true\n388:     rules:\n389:     - apiGroups:\n390:       - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n391:       resources:\n392:       - agentruntimes\n393:       - codeinterpreters\n394:       verbs:\n395:       - get\n396:       - list\n397:       - watch\n398:       - create\n399:       - update\n400:       - patch\n401:       - delete\n402:     - apiGroups:\n403:       - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n404:       resources:\n405:       - agentruntimes/status\n406:       - codeinterpreters/status\n407:       verbs:\n408:       - get\n409:       - update\n410:       - patch\n411:     - apiGroups:\n412:       - \"\"\n413:       resources:\n414:       - pods\n415:       - services\n416:       - configmaps\n417:       - secrets\n418:       verbs:\n419:       - get\n420:       - list\n421:       - watch\n422:       - create\n423:       - update\n424:       - patch\n425:       - delete\n426:     - apiGroups:\n427:       - \"\"\n428:       resources:\n429:       - pods/status\n430:       verbs:\n431:       - get\n432:     - apiGroups:\n433:       - \"\"\n434:       resources:\n435:       - events\n436:       verbs:\n437:       - create\n438:       - patch\n439: \n440: # Monitoring configuration\n441: monitoring:\n442:   enabled: false\n443:   serviceMonitor:\n444:     enabled: false\n445:     interval: 30s\n446:     scrapeTimeout: 10s\n447:     labels:\n448:       release: prometheus\n449:     annotations: {}\n450:     metricRelabelings: []\n451:     relabelings: []\n452:   prometheusRule:\n453:     enabled: false\n454:     labels:\n455:       release: prometheus\n456:     rules: []\n457: \n458: # ConfigMaps configuration\n459: configMaps:\n460:   agentcubeConfig:\n461:     create: true\n462:     data:\n463:       LOG_LEVEL: info\n464:       LOG_FORMAT: json\n465:       METRICS_ENABLED: \"true\"\n466:       METRICS_PORT: \"9090\"\n467:       TRACING_ENABLED: \"false\"\n468:       TRACING_ENDPOINT: \"\"\n469: \n470: # Secrets configuration\n471: secrets:\n472:   create: false\n473:   name: agentcube-secrets\n474:   data: {}\n475: \n476: # NetworkPolicies configuration\n477: networkPolicies:\n478:   enabled: false\n479:   defaultDeny: false\n480:   allowExternal: true\n481:   rules:\n482:     controllerManager:\n483:       ingress:\n484:       - from:\n485:         - podSelector:\n486:             matchLabels:\n487:               app.kubernetes.io/component: workload-manager\n488:         ports:\n489:         - port: 8080\n490:           protocol: TCP\n491:       egress:\n492:       - to:\n493:         - namespaceSelector: {}\n494:         ports:\n495:         - port: 443\n496:           protocol: TCP\n497:     workloadManager:\n498:       ingress:\n499:       - from:\n500:         - podSelector:\n501:             matchLabels:\n502:               app.kubernetes.io/component: router\n503:         ports:\n504:         - port: 8080\n505:           protocol: TCP\n506:       egress:\n507:       - to:\n508:         - namespaceSelector: {}\n509:         ports:\n510:         - port: 443\n511:           protocol: TCP\n512:     router:\n513:       ingress:\n514:       - from:\n515:         - namespaceSelector: {}\n516:         ports:\n517:         - port: 8080\n518:           protocol: TCP\n519:       egress:\n520:       - to:\n521:         - podSelector:\n522:             matchLabels:\n523:               app.kubernetes.io/component: workload-manager\n524:         ports:\n525:         - port: 8080\n526:           protocol: TCP\n527: \n528: # Ingress configuration\n529: ingress:\n530:   enabled: false\n531:   className: nginx\n532:   annotations:\n533:     cert-manager.io/cluster-issuer: letsencrypt-prod\n534:   hosts:\n535:     - host: agentcube.example.com\n536:       paths:\n537:         - path: /\n538:           pathType: Prefix\n539:           backend:\n540:             service:\n541:               name: router\n542:               port:\n543:                 number: 8080\n544:   tls:\n545:     - secretName: agentcube-tls\n546:       hosts:\n547:         - agentcube.example.com\n548: \n549: # Pod priority and preemption\n550: priorityClassName: \"\"\n551: \n552: # Extra manifests to include\n553: extraManifests: []\n554: \n555: # Post-install, pre-upgrade, post-upgrade hooks\n556: hooks:\n557:   preInstall:\n558:     enabled: false\n559:     image: busybox:latest\n560:     command: []\n561:   postInstall:\n562:     enabled: false\n563:     image: busybox:latest\n564:     command: []\n565:   preUpgrade:\n566:     enabled: false\n567:     image: busybox:latest\n568:     command: []\n569:   postUpgrade:\n570:     enabled: false\n571:     image: busybox:latest\n572:     command: []\n573: ```\n574: \n575: ### Helper Templates (_helpers.tpl)\n576: \n577: ```yaml\n578: {{/*\n579: Expand the name of the chart.\n580: */}}\n581: {{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n582: {{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n583: {{- end }}\n584: \n585: {{/*\n586: Create a default fully qualified app name.\n587: */}}\n588: {{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n589: {{- if .Values.fullnameOverride }}\n590: {{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n591: {{- else }}\n592: {{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride }}\n593: {{- if contains $name .Release.Name }}\n594: {{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n595: {{- else }}\n596: {{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n597: {{- end }}\n598: {{- end }}\n599: {{- end }}\n600: \n601: {{/*\n602: Create chart name and version as used by the chart label.\n603: */}}\n604: {{- define \"agentcube.chart\" -}}\n605: {{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Chart.Name .Chart.Version | replace \"+\" \"_\" | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n606: {{- end }}\n607: \n608: {{/*\n609: Common labels\n610: */}}\n611: {{- define \"agentcube.labels\" -}}\n612: helm.sh/chart: {{ include \"agentcube.chart\" . }}\n613: {{ include \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" . }}\n614: {{- if .Chart.AppVersion }}\n615: app.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Chart.AppVersion | quote }}\n616: {{- end }}\n617: app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}\n618: {{- end }}\n619: \n620: {{/*\n621: Selector labels\n622: */}}\n623: {{- define \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" -}}\n624: app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n625: app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n626: {{- end }}\n627: \n628: {{/*\n629: Create the name of the service account to use\n630: */}}\n631: {{- define \"agentcube.controllerManager.serviceAccountName\" -}}\n632: {{- if .Values.controllerManager.serviceAccount.create }}\n633: {{- default (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .) .Values.controllerManager.serviceAccount.name }}\n634: {{- else }}\n635: {{- default \"default\" .Values.controllerManager.serviceAccount.name }}\n636: {{- end }}\n637: {{- end }}\n638: \n639: {{/*\n640: Create the name of the service account to use\n641: */}}\n642: {{- define \"agentcube.workloadManager.serviceAccountName\" -}}\n643: {{- if .Values.workloadManager.serviceAccount.create }}\n644: {{- default (printf \"%s-workload-manager\" (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .)) .Values.workloadManager.serviceAccount.name }}\n645: {{- else }}\n646: {{- default \"default\" .Values.workloadManager.serviceAccount.name }}\n647: {{- end }}\n648: {{- end }}\n649: \n650: {{/*\n651: Create the name of the service account to use\n652: */}}\n653: {{- define \"agentcube.router.serviceAccountName\" -}}\n654: {{- if .Values.router.serviceAccount.create }}\n655: {{- default (printf \"%s-router\" (include \"agentcube.fullname\" .)) .Values.router.serviceAccount.name }}\n656: {{- else }}\n657: {{- default \"default\" .Values.router.serviceAccount.name }}\n658: {{- end }}\n659: {{- end }}\n660: \n661: {{/*\n662: Image registry helper\n663: */}}\n664: {{- define \"agentcube.imageRegistry\" -}}\n665: {{- .Values.global.imageRegistry | default \"\" -}}\n666: {{- end }}\n667: \n668: {{/*\n669: Build fully qualified image reference\n670: */}}\n671: {{- define \"agentcube.image\" -}}\n672: {{- $registry := include \"agentcube.imageRegistry\" . -}}\n673: {{- if $registry }}\n674: {{- printf \"%s/%s:%s\" $registry .repository .tag }}\n675: {{- else }}\n676: {{- printf \"%s:%s\" .repository .tag }}\n677: {{- end }}\n678: {{- end }}\n679: ```\n680: \n681: ## API Contracts\n682: \n683: ### Template: CRD Installation\n684: \n685: **File:** `templates/crds/agentruntime.yaml`\n686: \n687: ```yaml\n688: {{- if .Values.controllerManager.enabled }}\n689: apiVersion: apiextensions.k8s.io/v1\n690: kind: CustomResourceDefinition\n691: metadata:\n692:   name: agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n693:   annotations:\n694:     helm.sh/hook: crd-install\n695:     helm.sh/hook-weight: \"-5\"\n696:     helm.sh/hook-delete-policy: before-hook-creation\n697:   labels:\n698:     {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\n699: spec:\n700:   group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n701:   names:\n702:     kind: AgentRuntime\n703:     listKind: AgentRuntimeList\n704:     plural: agentruntimes\n705:     shortNames:\n706:     - art\n707:     singular: agentruntime\n708:   scope: Namespaced\n709:   versions:\n710:   - name: v1alpha1\n711:     served: true\n712:     storage: true\n713:     schema:\n714:       openAPIV3Schema:\n715:         type: object\n716:         properties:\n717:           apiVersion:\n718:             type: string\n719:           kind:\n720:             type: string\n721:           metadata:\n722:             type: object\n723:           spec:\n724:             type: object\n725:             properties:\n726:               maxSessionDuration:\n727:                 type: string\n728:                 default: \"8h\"\n729:               sessionTimeout:\n730:                 type: string\n731:                 default: \"15m\"\n732:               podTemplate:\n733:                 type: object\n734:                 properties:\n735:                   metadata:\n736:                     type: object\n737:                   spec:\n738:                     type: object\n739:               targetPort:\n740:                 type: array\n741:                 items:\n742:                   type: object\n743:                   properties:\n744:                     port:\n745:                       type: integer\n746:                       format: int32\n747:                     protocol:\n748:                       type: string\n749:                       enum: [\"HTTP\", \"HTTPS\"]\n750:                     pathPrefix:\n751:                       type: string\n752:                     name:\n753:                       type: string\n754:                 required: [\"port\", \"protocol\"]\n755:             required: [\"maxSessionDuration\", \"sessionTimeout\", \"podTemplate\", \"targetPort\"]\n756:           status:\n757:             type: object\n758:             properties:\n759:               conditions:\n760:                 type: array\n761:                 items:\n762:                   type: object\n763:                   properties:\n764:                     lastTransitionTime:\n765:                       format: date-time\n766:                       type: string\n767:                     message:\n768:                       type: string\n769:                     reason:\n770:                       type: string\n771:                     status:\n772:                       type: string\n773:                     type:\n774:                       type: string\n775:                     observedGeneration:\n776:                       format: int64\n777:                       type: integer\n778:               observedGeneration:\n779:                 format: int64\n780:                 type: integer\n781:     subresources:\n782:       status: {}\n783:     additionalPrinterColumns:\n784:     - name: Age\n785:       type: date\n786:       jsonPath: .metadata.creationTimestamp\n787: {{- end }}\n788: ```\n789: \n790: ### Template: Controller Manager Deployment\n791: \n792: **File:** `templates/controller-manager/deployment.yaml`\n793: \n794: ```yaml\n795: {{- if .Values.controllerManager.enabled }}\n796: apiVersion: apps/v1\n797: kind: Deployment\n798: metadata:\n799:   name: {{ include \"agentcube.fullname\" . }}\n800:   namespace: {{ include \"agentcube.namespace\" . }}\n801:   labels:\n802:     {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}\n803:     app.kubernetes.io/component: controller-manager\n804: spec:\n805:   replicas: {{ .Values.controllerManager.replicaCount }}\n806:   selector:\n807:     matchLabels:\n808:       {{- include \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" . | nindent 6 }}\n809:       app.kubernetes.io/component: controller-manager\n810:   template:\n811:     metadata:\n812:       annotations:\n813:         checksum/config: {{ include (print $.Template.BasePath \"/configmaps/config.yaml\") . | sha256sum }}\n814:         {{- with .Values.controllerManager.podAnnotations }}\n815:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n816:         {{- end }}\n817:       labels:\n818:         {{- include \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" . | nindent 8 }}\n819:         app.kubernetes.io/component: controller-manager\n820:         {{- with .Values.controllerManager.podLabels }}\n821:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n822:         {{- end }}\n823:     spec:\n824:       {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n825:       imagePullSecrets:\n826:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n827:       {{- end }}\n828:       serviceAccountName: {{ include \"agentcube.controllerManager.serviceAccountName\" . }}\n829:       securityContext:\n830:         {{- toYaml .Values.controllerManager.securityContext | nindent 8 }}\n831:       {{- with .Values.controllerManager.nodeSelector }}\n832:       nodeSelector:\n833:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n834:       {{- end }}\n835:       {{- with .Values.controllerManager.affinity }}\n836:       affinity:\n837:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n838:       {{- end }}\n839:       {{- with .Values.controllerManager.tolerations }}\n840:       tolerations:\n841:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n842:       {{- end }}\n843:       {{- if .Values.priorityClassName }}\n844:       priorityClassName: {{ .Values.priorityClassName }}\n845:       {{- end }}\n846:       containers:\n847:       - name: controller-manager\n848:         securityContext:\n849:           {{- toYaml .Values.controllerManager.containerSecurityContext | nindent 10 }}\n850:         image: \"{{ include \"agentcube.image\" (dict \"registry\" .Values.global.imageRegistry \"repository\" .Values.controllerManager.image.repository \"tag\" .Values.controllerManager.image.tag) }}\"\n851:         imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.controllerMan